description.excerpt:
Code release for "Unsupervised Multi-Class Domain Adaptation: Theory, Algorithms, and Practice", which is 
an extension of our preliminary work of SymmNets [Paper] [Code]

All expeimental results are logged in the file of "./experiments" 
Codes of McDalNets -->./solver/McDalNet_solver.py 
Codes of SymNets-V2
TPAMI2020  "Unsupervised Multi-Class Domain Adaptation: Theory, Algorithms, and Practice"
